divs: Sighting Details I took two pictures of the trees and clowds behind my house but didn't see the pictures until September 9 2008 and that was when I first noticed the Object. The pictures were taken no more than 5 seconds apart or less and the Object only appeared in the first Picture. The camera I used was a Sony Cybershot 2.1 Mega Pixel Model DSC-S50.
